            "detailed_description": "Ys returns with a brand new adventure for the first time in 8 years! Adol awakens shipwrecked and stranded on a cursed island. There, he and the other shipwrecked passengers he rescues form a village to challenge fearsome beasts and mysterious ruins on the isolated island. Amidst this, Adol begins to dream of a mysterious blue-haired maiden living in an unknown world. Join Adol as he unravels the riddle of the cursed isle and the blue-haired maiden Dana in <i>Ys VIII: Lacrimosa of DANA</i>!<br><br><strong>Key Features:<br>An Epic Tale</strong> - Follow Adol on his latest adventure and uncover the mysteries of the cursed island.<br><br><strong>Party On!</strong> – Change your playable character on-the-fly as you battle ferocious foes in lightning-fast combat.<br><br><strong>Another Side</strong> – Unravel the mystery of the blue-haired maiden Dana through her unique gameplay sections.<br><br><strong>It Takes a Village!</strong> – Rescue your fellow shipwrecked passengers and bring them to your village where they will provide valuable services.",
